// Coverage: all 77 Czech okresy (76 + Praha), 13074 katastrální území.
// Praha k.ú. carry an empty OKRES_NAZEV in the source and are normalised to "Praha"
// to match DISTRICTS in ./districts.ts. Every okres value here slugifies (via
// slugifyCs from @czagents/shared) to exactly the same slug as DISTRICTS.
//
// Stored grouped by okres (value-deduped) to stay compact; flat lookup maps are
// built once at module load.
//
// Resolution strategy for the ISIR dražební-vyhláška parser:
//   1. k.ú. name -> KATASTR_OKRES   (preferred: k.ú. names are globally unique)
//   2. obec name -> OBEC_OKRES       (only obce whose name maps to a single okres;
//                                     590 ambiguous names are
//                                     omitted on purpose — fail loudly, do NOT guess)
// Regenerate: re-download the ČÚZK zip and re-run the DE-RISK Task 2 generator.

